        Download

  %section.span6
    %header
      %h3
        #{jbtcore_current_stable_release.build_info.name} #{jbtcore_current_stable_release.build_info.version}
        - unless jbtcore_current_stable_release.build_info.build_type_label.nil?
          %span{:class=>"label label_#{jbtcore_current_stable_release.build_info.build_type_label}"}
            #{site.labels[jbtcore_current_stable_release.build_info.build_type_label]}
    .item
      :markdown
        * Individual plugins for Eclipse, including experimental plugins
        * Install into existing Eclipse only
        * Some assembly required
